Class Phptasks

java.lang.Object
  com.mk4droid.IMC_Store.Phptasks

public class Phptasks
extends java.lang.Object

These constants are related to the php in joomla component. They are called from mobile and they return JSON formatted string. Do not modify.

Author:
Dimitrios Ververidis, Dr. Post-doctoral Researcher, Information Technologies Institute, ITI-CERTH, Thermi, Thessaloniki, Greece ververid@iti.gr, http://mklab.iti.gr
